_pdbx_database_remark.text   
;
HETEROGEN
PROTEIN WAS CO-CRYSTALLIZED WITH THE PRO-DRUG QUERCETIN,
UNDERGOING FAST HYDROLYSIS IN SOLUTION (P.J. MULHOLLAND
ET AL., 2001). THE LIGAND DENSITY WAS MODELLED AS QUERCETIN,
AN EXTRA DENSITY PRESENT ABOVE THE C17 HYDROXYL GROUP IS
INCONSISTENT WITH THE PRO-DRUG STRUCTURE PUBLISHED AND WAS
